        {
            "title": "財經｜藥明生物(02269)去年盈利升46%",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"財經｜藥明生物(02269)去年盈利升46%\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"502\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/La7gZ15XzW1pdZUwE2YseQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUwMg--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/fortune_insight_694/dbddec0f78d2a1ab4bc25a6950c04ffb\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">財經｜藥明生物(02269)去年盈利升46%</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">藥明生物(02269)公布，截至去年底止全年股東應佔盈利49.08億元(人民幣‧下同)，按年升46.25%；每股基本盈利1.22元，不派末期息。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">按非國際財務報告準則指標，股東應佔經調整盈利56.4億元，按年升17.9%；經調整每股基本盈利1.4元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">期內，收益217.9億元，按年升16.68%；毛利率46%，升5個百分點，增幅主要得益於高利潤率的業務佔比提升、產能利用率提高，以及WBS和數字化舉措帶來的效率提升。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">展望2026年，該集團表示，將通過戰略投資前沿技術進一步加強其一體化平台，亦將優化全球產能布局。將致力於通過擁抱數字化創新(比如一站式客戶服務系統、實驗室核心管理系統和電子批記錄系統(EBR))、實施WBS精益管理及恪守最高合規標準，實現效率與卓越運營。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93-%E8%97%A5%E6%98%8E%E7%94%9F%E7%89%A9-02269-%E5%8E%BB%E5%B9%B4%E7%9B%88%E5%88%A9%E5%8D%8746-103128802.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-24 18:35:47",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "短炒波士｜港股能否企穩分水嶺成關鍵 決定跌勢｜Ringo",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/FcxZCYBWwlqD2SCED6nQUw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/bossmind_356/7964e8065a13a3d05a89e434d85b5f91\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國總統特朗普稱與伊朗的對話進展良好，但伊朗則否認與美國曾進行會談，美伊局勢仍存在高度不明朗。恒指周一急瀉近900點，插穿俗稱「牛熊分界線」的250天，失守兩萬五水平。兩萬五是恒指長期的分水嶺，若短中期未能收復企穩，整體跌勢或會持續。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">隨著特朗普稱將攻擊伊朗發電廠的期限延遲5天，環球股市出現大反彈。恒指周二升近700點，成功重上兩萬五，但要繼續觀察能否持續企穩。本月下方支持位料介乎23800點至24000點。由於周二恒指已有明顯反彈，但美伊局勢仍變幻莫測，投資者現階段應先採觀望態度，待局勢明顯轉變得明朗，才再作部署。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-78763045-c1cd-363b-ad6f-cc33ec36f711-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">部份個股已出現買入機會。騰訊（700）在500元水平表現硬淨，相信較難跌穿，上望有機會達560元，盈虧比具值搏率。阿里（9988）料能守於120元，短期或可反彈至130元，但整體走勢較弱，只宜作短炒，若跌穿110元便要止蝕。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">環球央行因油價上漲而有機會加息，導致金價走勢疲弱。黃金短期低位在每盎司4,100美元，在4,500美元以下可逐步吸納。貴金屬股紫金礦業（2899）周二大幅反彈超過7%，現估值雖不貴，但技術走勢仍欠佳，短期升至阻力位36至37元後，有機會再出現調整。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>Ringo<br/>資深投資者<br/>註：專欄作家言論不代表本網立場</strong></p><a class=\"mb-module-gap\" data-ylk=\"elm:img;elmt:link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;\" href=\"https://signup.hkiei.com/ringo_webinar_bossmind\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"686\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/ImrasCUjN02l5wpgg5PUdQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY4Ng--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/bossmind_356/f52012128630469615370091d56ff897\" width=\"960\"/></div></a></div>",
